snippet.title: Blockbuster Inc. Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist now:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1793090/Blockbuster_Inc/
Discord: https://discord.gg/P5fN48xp
Facebook page:  https://www.facebook.com/Blockbuster-Inc-104202058732963
Website:  https://blockbusterincgame.com/

In Blockbuster Inc. you will take total control of your very own movie studio. You will be able to construct all the facilities, hire and manage all sorts of employees and stars with the aim to produce the most prolific films and Tv.
